<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="what-for">what (…) for</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>为什么：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His mother told him to put on his hat. “What for?” he asked. 
他母亲让他戴上帽子。“带帽子干什么？”他问道。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What did you do that for? 
你为什么要那么做呢？</p></div></div>